How can I justify supporting a government that has been the source of multiple global conflicts since the end of the Second World War?  How can I trust a government that spins such an obscene amount of propaganda to support its actions?  How can I support a government that is YET AGAIN RATTLING SABERS IN THE NAME OF WORLD PEACE.<br>
<br>
I remember when the western propaganda machine used to paint USSR in exactly the same light.  Crazy commies, world domination and they are all hoisting nuclear missiles, chugging vodka and goose stepping up and down Red Square.  It's the same fucking bullshit all over again, the problem is most of you don't care much for history to see the parallels between what happened in the past and what happening now.  Ivory towers?  Hardly.<br>
<br>
I love it how the media is saying that it is the onset of another Cold War and the administration naturally rolls out the PR bozos and claims that it wants to avoid a Cold War, yet it is doing everything possible to ensure another Cold War.<br>
<br>
<br>
At any rate, these facts are indisputable.  In fact, I sometimes grow weary of stating the obvious for you, peons.  What I am more interested in is &quot;why?&quot;.  Oil, national prestige, to stimulate economy.  Who knows?  Or maybe Bush truly believes in what he is doing is the right thing but he is too narrow sighted to see the repercussions that will come in years to pass.<br>
<br>
