Now here is another revelation for you, the U.S. has never done anything that isn't motivated by self interest.  Now you're going to tell me, &quot;what is wrong with that?&quot;.  There is nothing wrong with that.  But that is not what you spin to the media.  How many times has the government trotted out the same tired line about protecting sovereignty, freedom, democracy, etc.?  Far too many to count - yet none of American actions are motivated by those noble ideals.  I guess what I am trying to illuminate for you in a long round-about way is that YOU ARE A BUNCH OF FUCKING HYPOCRITES.  And hence your word is no better than that of the Bin ladens, Saddams and the Kims and whoever is the next fad bad guy is, yet you attempt to hold them to higher standards.<br>
